OTRS Joomla Gateway
===================

This is the Cognidox Ltd OTRS Joomla gateway. It can be used to connect
a Joomla site with the customer user ticket side of an OTRS installation.

It is distributed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3:
http://www.opensource.org/licenses/agpl-v3.html

This repository holds:

    com_otrsgateway    - Joomla component and plugin sources
    otrs_joomla_module - OTRS component sources

Installation packages for both the Joomla and OTRS components are provided
in the Files section of the Github repository.

More information about installation and usage can be found on the Cognidox
project page: 
http://www.cognidox.com/opensource/otrs-joomla-gateway
